<UserControl xmlns="https://github.com/avaloniaui"
             xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
             x:Class="AndroidSample.Avalonia.Views.SplashDemoView">
    <DockPanel Margin="16">
        <StackPanel DockPanel.Dock="Top" Spacing="8">
            <TextBlock Text="3. 启动页与开机动画" FontSize="20" FontWeight="Bold"/>
            <Button Content="← 返回" Click="OnBack"/>
        </StackPanel>

        <ScrollViewer>
            <StackPanel Spacing="12">
                <TextBlock TextWrapping="Wrap" FontSize="14">
Android 原生 Splash 已在 SplashActivity.cs 中配置：
• 主题 @style/MyTheme.Splash（windowBackground 指向 splash_background.xml）
• MainLauncher=true，NoHistory=true
• 淡入动画 1.5 s 后跳转 MainActivity
                </TextBlock>

                <TextBlock Text="演示：Avalonia 内部淡入动画" FontWeight="Bold"/>
                <Border x:Name="AnimBox" Height="120" CornerRadius="12"
                        Background="#1565C0" Opacity="0">
                    <TextBlock Text="✓ Avalonia 过渡动画"
                               Foreground="White" FontSize="18"
                               HorizontalAlignment="Center"
                               VerticalAlignment="Center"/>
                </Border>
                <Button Content="播放动画" Click="OnPlay" HorizontalAlignment="Center"/>
            </StackPanel>
        </ScrollViewer>
    </DockPanel>
</UserControl>
